Why this license
----------------
The English source instructions are drawn from wikiHow, which publishes its
content under CC BY-NC-SA 3.0. The ShareAlike term requires that derivative
works — including translations — carry the same license. NonCommercial use
only. Attribution to wikiHow (and to this corpus) is required.

How the data is released (rehydration)
--------------------------------------
To respect the source license, this repository does NOT redistribute the
English wikiHow text. The corpus is released by *rehydration*:

  * the Myanmar post-edited translations,
  * the source article URLs / identifiers, and
  * the build script (`src/data/build_splits.py`)

are published so the aligned English–Myanmar pairs can be reconstructed
locally. The raw and processed parallel files are intentionally excluded from
version control (see `.gitignore`).

